mixin mcq-2-3()
  main.sub
    .containers
      #Section1.tabcontent
        ul.quiz
          li.quiz-box
            h3 Question1: When will the next halving take place?
            ul.choices
              li.answer-box
                label
                  input(type='radio' name='question1' value='buffer')
                  span Around April 11th, 2024
              li.answer-box
                label
                  input(type='radio' name='question1' value='function')
                  span Around December 2nd, 2022
              li.answer-box
                label
                  input(type='radio' name='question1' value='global')
                  span Around June 10th, 2023
              li.answer-box
                label
                  input(type='radio' name='question1' value='number')
                  span Around the end of February 1st, 2024


          li.quiz-box
            h3 Question2: Why can it take more or less time than 10 minutes to generate a new Bitcoin block?
            ul.choices
              li.answer-box
                label
                  input(type='radio' name='question1' value='buffer')
                  span the underlying algorithm that governs the block generation generates random outputs
              li.answer-box
                label
                  input(type='radio' name='question1' value='function')
                  span creating a valid block depends on solving a crossword puzzle
              li.answer-box
                label
                  input(type='radio' name='question1' value='global')
                  span transaction fees are volatile


          li.quiz-box
            h3 Question3: Trusted third parties like an acquirer, issuer and payment network involved in a transaction in a brick-and-mortar store, are usually also involved in an e-commerce transaction.
            ul.choices
              li.answer-box
                label
                  input(type='radio' name='question1' value='buffer')
                  span True
              li.answer-box
                label
                  input(type='radio' name='question1' value='function')
                  span False


          li.quiz-box
            h3 Question4: Within the Bitcoin network, you donâ€™t have to trust anyone to process your transactions.
            ul.choices
              li.answer-box
                label
                  input(type='radio' name='question1' value='buffer')
                  span True
              li.answer-box
                label
                  input(type='radio' name='question1' value='function')
                  span False


        .button-box
          button.view-results#viewResults View Results
          span#myresults.my-results My results will appear here
          span#myresultsDescription.my-results-description Description
